{
  "video_id": "ez7HOFKTtH0",
  "title": "The fascinating science of bubbles, from soap to champagne | Li Wei Tan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12772.0,
      "end_time": 15555.0,
      "text": "Some years ago, I was visiting Paris"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15579.0,
      "end_time": 19904.0,
      "text": "and walking along the Seine River during a beautiful summer afternoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19928.0,
      "end_time": 23177.0,
      "text": "I saw giant bubbles floating on the riverbank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23201.0,
      "end_time": 24612.0,
      "text": "like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24636.0,
      "end_time": 27589.0,
      "text": "The next moment, it popped and was gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28273.0,
      "end_time": 32289.0,
      "text": "Making them were two street performers surrounded by a crowd."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32845.0,
      "end_time": 36244.0,
      "text": "They visibly make a living by asking for donations"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36268.0,
      "end_time": 40128.0,
      "text": "and by selling pairs of sticks tied with two strings."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40152.0,
      "end_time": 45219.0,
      "text": "When I was there, a man bought a pair of sticks for 10 euros,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45243.0,
      "end_time": 46995.0,
      "text": "which surprised me."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47773.0,
      "end_time": 51686.0,
      "text": "I am a scientist who is passionate about bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51710.0,
      "end_time": 55660.0,
      "text": "I know the right trick to make the giant bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55900.0,
      "end_time": 58491.0,
      "text": "is the right soapy water mixture itself --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58515.0,
      "end_time": 59946.0,
      "text": "not the sticks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59970.0,
      "end_time": 61281.0,
      "text": "which may be needed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61305.0,
      "end_time": 63448.0,
      "text": "but you can easily make them at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63924.0,
      "end_time": 69566.0,
      "text": "Focusing on the sticks makes us not see that the real tool is the bubble itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70970.0,
      "end_time": 75102.0,
      "text": "Bubbles might seem like something just children make while playing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76117.0,
      "end_time": 78540.0,
      "text": "but sometimes it can be really stunning."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79659.0,
      "end_time": 83997.0,
      "text": "However, there are more fascinating science to bubbles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84210.0,
      "end_time": 86668.0,
      "text": "such as problem-solving tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87192.0,
      "end_time": 89565.0,
      "text": "So I would like to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 89589.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "a few stories about the science of creating bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 93284.0,
      "end_time": 97279.0,
      "text": "and the science of eliminating the microscopic ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97742.0,
      "end_time": 101660.0,
      "text": "Since it&#39;s up on the screen, let&#39;s start with the soap bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 102478.0,
      "end_time": 105524.0,
      "text": "It is made from very common substances:"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105548.0,
      "end_time": 109325.0,
      "text": "air, water, soap, in the right mixture."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 110214.0,
      "end_time": 113815.0,
      "text": "You can see soap bubbles constantly changing their colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 113839.0,
      "end_time": 118336.0,
      "text": "This is due to the interaction with light at various directions"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 118360.0,
      "end_time": 120477.0,
      "text": "and the changes of their thickness."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121471.0,
      "end_time": 125230.0,
      "text": "One of the common substances, water molecules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125254.0,
      "end_time": 131651.0,
      "text": "are formed by two atoms of hydrogen and one atom of oxygen -- H2O."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 132350.0,
      "end_time": 137141.0,
      "text": "On most surfaces, water droplets tend to curve inwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 137165.0,
      "end_time": 139537.0,
      "text": "forming a semihemisphere shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 140237.0,
      "end_time": 145700.0,
      "text": "This is because the water droplet&#39;s surface is like an elastic sheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 145729.0,
      "end_time": 149753.0,
      "text": "The water molecule on the surface is constantly being pulled inwards"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 149777.0,
      "end_time": 151698.0,
      "text": "by the molecule at the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 152826.0,
      "end_time": 157850.0,
      "text": "And the quality of the elasticity is what we call \"surface tension.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 158422.0,
      "end_time": 160472.0,
      "text": "Now by adding soap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 160497.0,
      "end_time": 165410.0,
      "text": "what happens is the soap molecule reduces the surface tension of water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 165650.0,
      "end_time": 168989.0,
      "text": "making it more elastic and easier to form bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 170505.0,
      "end_time": 175224.0,
      "text": "You can think of a bubble as a mathematical problem-solver."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 175779.0,
      "end_time": 180821.0,
      "text": "You see it relentlessly trying to achieve geometry perfection."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 180845.0,
      "end_time": 186657.0,
      "text": "For instance, a sphere is the shape with the least surface area"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 186681.0,
      "end_time": 188298.0,
      "text": "for a given volume."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 188322.0,
      "end_time": 192666.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why a single bubble is always in the shape of a sphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 192690.0,
      "end_time": 194526.0,
      "text": "Let me show you. Check it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 210112.0,
      "end_time": 211930.0,
      "text": "This is a single bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 211954.0,
      "end_time": 214221.0,
      "text": "When two bubbles touch each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 217437.0,
      "end_time": 220671.0,
      "text": "they can save materials by sharing a common wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 228385.0,
      "end_time": 231310.0,
      "text": "When more and more bubbles are added together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 231334.0,
      "end_time": 233163.0,
      "text": "their geometry changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 233556.0,
      "end_time": 235915.0,
      "text": "These four bubbles are added together."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 235939.0,
      "end_time": 238209.0,
      "text": "They meet at one point at the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 282871.0,
      "end_time": 285241.0,
      "text": "When six bubbles are added together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 285265.0,
      "end_time": 287905.0,
      "text": "a magical cube appears at the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 287929.0,
      "end_time": 291556.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 295590.0,
      "end_time": 297742.0,
      "text": "That is surface tension at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 297766.0,
      "end_time": 301704.0,
      "text": "trying to find the most effective geometry arrangement."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 303693.0,
      "end_time": 308198.0,
      "text": "Now, let me give you another example."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 309153.0,
      "end_time": 312155.0,
      "text": "This is a very simple prop."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 313258.0,
      "end_time": 317166.0,
      "text": "This is made from two layers of plastic"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 317190.0,
      "end_time": 319676.0,
      "text": "with four pins connected to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 319700.0,
      "end_time": 325690.0,
      "text": "Imagine these four pins represent four cities that are equally apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 325714.0,
      "end_time": 329419.0,
      "text": "and we would like to make roads to connect these four cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 330426.0,
      "end_time": 334669.0,
      "text": "My question is: What is the shortest length to connect these four cities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 335723.0,
      "end_time": 339624.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s find out the answer by dipping it into the soapy water."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 343775.0,
      "end_time": 349298.0,
      "text": "Remember, the soap bubble forms will always try to minimize"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 349322.0,
      "end_time": 350922.0,
      "text": "their surface area"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 350946.0,
      "end_time": 353652.0,
      "text": "with a perfect geometry arrangement."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 354632.0,
      "end_time": 359741.0,
      "text": "So the solution might not be something you expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 362175.0,
      "end_time": 365583.0,
      "text": "The shortest length to connect these four cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 365607.0,
      "end_time": 371471.0,
      "text": "is 2.73 times the distance between these two cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 371495.0,
      "end_time": 375788.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 377401.0,
      "end_time": 379367.0,
      "text": "Now you&#39;ve got the idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 379391.0,
      "end_time": 384670.0,
      "text": "The soap bubble forms will always try to minimize their surface area"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 384694.0,
      "end_time": 387980.0,
      "text": "with a perfect geometry arrangement."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 389416.0,
      "end_time": 395289.0,
      "text": "Now, let us look at bubbles in another perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 396357.0,
      "end_time": 400265.0,
      "text": "My daughter, Zoe, loves visiting zoos."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 400289.0,
      "end_time": 406217.0,
      "text": "Her favorite spot is Penguin Cove at Marwell Zoo in Southern England,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 406242.0,
      "end_time": 410674.0,
      "text": "where she could see penguins swim at speed under the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 411653.0,
      "end_time": 415432.0,
      "text": "One day, she noticed that the body of penguins"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 415456.0,
      "end_time": 418456.0,
      "text": "leaves a trail of bubbles when they swim"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 418480.0,
      "end_time": 420360.0,
      "text": "and asked why."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 420384.0,
      "end_time": 423351.0,
      "text": "Animals and birds like penguins"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 423375.0,
      "end_time": 426873.0,
      "text": "that spend a lot of their time under the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 426897.0,
      "end_time": 433312.0,
      "text": "have evolved an ingenious way of utilizing the capability of bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 433336.0,
      "end_time": 435942.0,
      "text": "to reduce the density of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 437660.0,
      "end_time": 441777.0,
      "text": "Emperor penguins are thought to be able to dive a few hundred meters"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 441802.0,
      "end_time": 443909.0,
      "text": "below the sea surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 444562.0,
      "end_time": 448254.0,
      "text": "They are thought to store the air under their feathers"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 448278.0,
      "end_time": 449933.0,
      "text": "before they dive"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 449957.0,
      "end_time": 454726.0,
      "text": "and then progressively release it as a cloud of bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 455300.0,
      "end_time": 458968.0,
      "text": "This reduces the density of water surrounding them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 458992.0,
      "end_time": 461777.0,
      "text": "making it easier to swim through"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 461801.0,
      "end_time": 466630.0,
      "text": "and speed up their swimming speed at least 40 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 467779.0,
      "end_time": 471508.0,
      "text": "This feature has been noticed by the ship manufacturers."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 472364.0,
      "end_time": 475852.0,
      "text": "I am talking about the big ships here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 475877.0,
      "end_time": 480884.0,
      "text": "the ones that are used to transport thousands of containers across the ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 481559.0,
      "end_time": 486961.0,
      "text": "Recently, they developed a system called \"air lubricating system,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 486985.0,
      "end_time": 488950.0,
      "text": "inspired by the penguins."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 489704.0,
      "end_time": 493870.0,
      "text": "In this system, they produce a lot of air bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 493894.0,
      "end_time": 497983.0,
      "text": "and redistribute them across the whole of the ship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 498700.0,
      "end_time": 502567.0,
      "text": "like an air carpet that reduces the water resistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 502591.0,
      "end_time": 504778.0,
      "text": "when a ship is moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 506167.0,
      "end_time": 510184.0,
      "text": "This feature cuts off the energy consumption for the ship"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 510209.0,
      "end_time": 512826.0,
      "text": "up to 15 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 514847.0,
      "end_time": 518363.0,
      "text": "Bubbles can also be used for medicines."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 518388.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521268.00000000006,
      "text": "It can also play a role in medicines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 522889.0,
      "end_time": 529858.0,
      "text": "for instance, as a method for noninvasive delivery systems for drugs and genes"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 529882.0,
      "end_time": 532387.0,
      "text": "to a specific part of the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 532412.0,
      "end_time": 534468.0,
      "text": "Imagine a microbubble"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 534492.0,
      "end_time": 538589.0,
      "text": "filled with a mixture of drugs and magnetic agents"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 538613.0,
      "end_time": 541580.0,
      "text": "being injected into our bloodstream."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 542273.0,
      "end_time": 545685.0,
      "text": "The bubbles will move to the target areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 545709.0,
      "end_time": 548311.0,
      "text": "But how do they know where to go?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 548336.0,
      "end_time": 550452.0,
      "text": "Because we placed a magnet there."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 550476.0,
      "end_time": 552837.0,
      "text": "For instance, this part of my hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 552861.0,
      "end_time": 556872.0,
      "text": "When the microbubbles move to this part of my hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 556897.0,
      "end_time": 560688.0,
      "text": "we can pop it via ultrasound"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 560712.0,
      "end_time": 564210.0,
      "text": "and release the drug exactly where it&#39;s needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 565895.0,
      "end_time": 569369.0,
      "text": "Now, I mentioned about the science of creating bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 569393.0,
      "end_time": 573694.0,
      "text": "But sometimes we also need to remove them."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 573718.0,
      "end_time": 576170.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s actually part of my job."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 576731.0,
      "end_time": 581609.0,
      "text": "My exact job title is \"ink formulation scientist.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 581633.0,
      "end_time": 585683.0,
      "text": "But I don&#39;t work on the ink that you use for your writing pens."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 586366.0,
      "end_time": 589178.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m working on some cool applications"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 589202.0,
      "end_time": 593622.0,
      "text": "such as organic photovoltaics, OPVs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 593646.0,
      "end_time": 597318.0,
      "text": "and organic light-emitting diodes, OLEDs."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 597342.0,
      "end_time": 603622.0,
      "text": "Part of my job is to figure out how and why we want to remove the bubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 603646.0,
      "end_time": 606132.0,
      "text": "from the ink that my company produces."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 606989.0,
      "end_time": 610251.0,
      "text": "During the formulation-mixing process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 610275.0,
      "end_time": 612340.0,
      "text": "or preparation process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 612580.0,
      "end_time": 618253.0,
      "text": "we mix active ingredients, solvents and additives"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 618277.0,
      "end_time": 622806.0,
      "text": "in order to achieve the formulations with the properties we want"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 622830.0,
      "end_time": 624466.0,
      "text": "when the ink is being used."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 625196.0,
      "end_time": 628113.0,
      "text": "But just like you would make drinks"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 628137.0,
      "end_time": 629406.0,
      "text": "or bake cakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 629431.0,
      "end_time": 634987.0,
      "text": "it is unavoidable that some air bubbles will be trapped inside that ink."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 635686.0,
      "end_time": 638948.0,
      "text": "Here, we are talking about a different space"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 638972.0,
      "end_time": 641841.0,
      "text": "from the bubbles I&#39;d seen in Paris."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 642960.0,
      "end_time": 645162.0,
      "text": "The bubbles that are trapped inside those inks"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 645186.0,
      "end_time": 648117.0,
      "text": "vary between a few millimeters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 648141.0,
      "end_time": 649384.0,
      "text": "a few microns"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 649408.0,
      "end_time": 652381.0,
      "text": "or even a few nanometers in size."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 652405.0,
      "end_time": 654328.0,
      "text": "And what we are concerned about"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 654352.0,
      "end_time": 657351.0,
      "text": "is the oxygen and the moisture that is trapped inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 658525.0,
      "end_time": 664230.0,
      "text": "At this size scale, removing them is not easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 664254.0,
      "end_time": 666186.0,
      "text": "But it matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 666210.0,
      "end_time": 670325.0,
      "text": "for instance, for organic light-emitting diodes inks"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 671772.0,
      "end_time": 678744.0,
      "text": "that we can use to produce display for your smartphone, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 679674.0,
      "end_time": 681909.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s supposed to last for many years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 681933.0,
      "end_time": 686953.0,
      "text": "but if the ink that we use has been absorbed with oxygen and moisture"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 686977.0,
      "end_time": 689340.0,
      "text": "[which] are not being removed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 689364.0,
      "end_time": 694234.0,
      "text": "then we can quickly see dark spots appear in the pixels."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 694943.0,
      "end_time": 701925.0,
      "text": "Now, one challenge we face in removing the microbubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 701950.0,
      "end_time": 705396.0,
      "text": "is that they are not very cooperative."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 705420.0,
      "end_time": 707367.0,
      "text": "They like to sit there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 707392.0,
      "end_time": 710278.0,
      "text": "bathing in the ink without moving much."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 710937.0,
      "end_time": 712899.0,
      "text": "But how do we kick them out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 714741.0,
      "end_time": 716836.0,
      "text": "One technology we use"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 716860.0,
      "end_time": 722401.0,
      "text": "is to force the ink going through a thin, long and tiny tube"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 722425.0,
      "end_time": 724555.0,
      "text": "with a porous wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 724580.0,
      "end_time": 727691.0,
      "text": "and we place the tubes inside the vacuum chamber,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 727715.0,
      "end_time": 732550.0,
      "text": "so that the bubbles can be squeezed out from the ink"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 732790.0,
      "end_time": 733434.0,
      "text": "and be removed."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 734730.0,
      "end_time": 740374.0,
      "text": "Once we manage to remove the bubbles from the ink that we produce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 741310.0,
      "end_time": 743695.0,
      "text": "it is time for celebration."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 745726.0,
      "end_time": 748741.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s open a bubbling champagne."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 755693.0,
      "end_time": 757881.0,
      "text": "Ooh, this is going to be fun!"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 757905.0,
      "end_time": 760890.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 762327.0,
      "end_time": 764657.0,
      "text": "Woooo!"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 764681.0,
      "end_time": 768387.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 772317.0,
      "end_time": 778450.0,
      "text": "You could see a lot of bubbles rushing out from the champagne bottle."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 778566.0,
      "end_time": 782909.0,
      "text": "These are the bubbles filled with carbon dioxide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 782933.0,
      "end_time": 788471.0,
      "text": "a gas that&#39;s been produced during the fermentation process of the wine."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 789226.0,
      "end_time": 790969.0,
      "text": "Let me pour some out."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 792919.0,
      "end_time": 794656.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t miss the chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 802292.0,
      "end_time": 804383.0,
      "text": "I guess it&#39;s enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 804407.0,
      "end_time": 805614.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 809178.0,
      "end_time": 814370.0,
      "text": "Here, I can see a lot of microbubbles"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 814394.0,
      "end_time": 819410.0,
      "text": "moving from the bottom of the glass to the top of the champagne."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 820286.0,
      "end_time": 821888.0,
      "text": "Before it pops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 822680.0,
      "end_time": 827877.0,
      "text": "it will jet tiny droplets of aroma molecules"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 827902.0,
      "end_time": 831573.0,
      "text": "and intensify the flavor of champagne,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 831597.0,
      "end_time": 835295.0,
      "text": "making us enjoy much more the flavor of champagne."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 836226.0,
      "end_time": 839728.0,
      "text": "As a scientist who is passionate about bubbles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 839752.0,
      "end_time": 841462.0,
      "text": "I love to see them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 842306.0,
      "end_time": 844441.0,
      "text": "I love to play with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 844465.0,
      "end_time": 846733.0,
      "text": "and I love to study them."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 846757.0,
      "end_time": 849800.0,
      "text": "And also, I love to drink them."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 849330.0,
      "end_time": 850242.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 850266.0,
      "end_time": 854728.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}